data.description: MOTIVATED SELLERS! Agents read comments!! This is a gorgeous updated and well kept home.Well maintained lawn with new sod, all new flower bed and magnolia tree, mulch and fruit trees (Orange, Lemon and mango).  A sprinkler system and privacy wall including gutters installed around the exterior. Beautiful sun room extension added for more FL sunshine. Brand new water softener system installed in the garage so that the life of the part can be endless. Maintenance has been well kept covering the pest control, true green and A/C. The A/C has brand new exterior siding for a great appeal. Interior has beautiful wood flooring, recess lighting and plant shelving, with linen closets and pantry for storage. The laundry room was converted to an in home office lowering the electric bill by placing the washer/dryer in the garage adding wood flooring around it. The room has the option to be converted back. Also assuring your buyer of a great purchase The Home Team performed drywall inspection. All fans and window coverings stay. If your ready for the best home on the market call and make your appointment today before its gone!! Ask about all the warranties and additional upgrades!
